name: San La Muerte / Holy slots
description:
San La Muerte's slot will give you money, love, health or... death! (yours? your enemy's?). But only if you're worthy of his powers. Depending on how many tokens you're holding from Chen's "Our Myths" gallery you'll get different results (if you're not synced it'll be random).

So make sure you go to https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/chen and collect'em all!

This piece is part of my contribution to "Our Myths" event held by Chen >>> https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/365336
